com.langtoun.oastypes

Interface OASObjectType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OASType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OASObjectTypeImpl

    public interface OASObjectType
extends OASType
    Public interface for OpenAPI specification object types. Objects of this type are derived from YAML like this: 
    
   type: object
   required: ...
   properties: ...
